19#include "PerspectiveTransform.h"

21#include <array>

24namespace ZXing {
25
26PerspectiveTransform PerspectiveTransform::inverse() const
27{
28 // Here, the adjoint serves as the inverse:
29 // Adjoint is the transpose of the cofactor matrix:
30 return {
31 a22 * a33 - a23 * a32,
32 a23 * a31 - a21 * a33,
33 a21 * a32 - a22 * a31,
34 a13 * a32 - a12 * a33,
35 a11 * a33 - a13 * a31,
36 a12 * a31 - a11 * a32,
37 a12 * a23 - a13 * a22,
38 a13 * a21 - a11 * a23,
39 a11 * a22 - a12 * a21
40 };
41}
42
43PerspectiveTransform PerspectiveTransform::times(const PerspectiveTransform& other) const
44{
45 return {
46 a11 * other.a11 + a21 * other.a12 + a31 * other.a13,
47 a11 * other.a21 + a21 * other.a22 + a31 * other.a23,
48 a11 * other.a31 + a21 * other.a32 + a31 * other.a33,
49 a12 * other.a11 + a22 * other.a12 + a32 * other.a13,
50 a12 * other.a21 + a22 * other.a22 + a32 * other.a23,
51 a12 * other.a31 + a22 * other.a32 + a32 * other.a33,
52 a13 * other.a11 + a23 * other.a12 + a33 * other.a13,
53 a13 * other.a21 + a23 * other.a22 + a33 * other.a23,
54 a13 * other.a31 + a23 * other.a32 + a33 * other.a33
55 };
56}
57
58PerspectiveTransform PerspectiveTransform::UnitSquareTo(const QuadrilateralF& q)
59{
60 //c++-17: structured binding
61 PointF::value_t x0, y0, x1, y1, x2, y2, x3, y3;
62 std::tie(x0, y0, x1, y1, x2, y2, x3, y3) =
63 std::tuple_cat(reinterpret_cast<const std::array<PointF::value_t, 8>&>(q));
64
65 auto d3 = q[0] - q[1] + q[2] - q[3];
66 if (d3 == PointF(0, 0)) {
67 // Affine
68 return {x1 - x0, x2 - x1, x0,
69 y1 - y0, y2 - y1, y0,
70 0.0f, 0.0f, 1.0f};
71 } else {
72 auto d1 = q[1] - q[2];
73 auto d2 = q[3] - q[2];
74 auto denominator = crossProduct(d1, d2);
75 auto a13 = crossProduct(d3, d2) / denominator;
76 auto a23 = crossProduct(d1, d3) / denominator;
77 return {x1 - x0 + a13 * x1, x3 - x0 + a23 * x3, x0,
78 y1 - y0 + a13 * y1, y3 - y0 + a23 * y3, y0,
79 a13, a23, 1.0f};
80 }
81}
82
83PerspectiveTransform::PerspectiveTransform(const QuadrilateralF& src, const QuadrilateralF& dst)
84{
85 if (!IsConvex(src) || !IsConvex(dst))
86 return;
87 *this = UnitSquareTo(dst).times(UnitSquareTo(src).inverse());
88}
89
90PointF PerspectiveTransform::operator()(PointF p) const
91{
92 auto denominator = a13 * p.x + a23 * p.y + a33;
93 return {(a11 * p.x + a21 * p.y + a31) / denominator, (a12 * p.x + a22 * p.y + a32) / denominator};
94}
